  "title": "[pagination]: error message displays stalled value",
  "body": "Hi,\r\njust to let you know that the documentation for cssClasses for the pagination widget is not correct.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/afc507c276fac38c0371f7fbb704383115631046/src/widgets/pagination/pagination.js#L92\r\n\r\nThe documentation say the parameter is named `itemNextPage` and in the code it's `nextPageItem`, same for `itemPreviousPage` which is `previousPageItem`.\r\n\r\nI think you may have others typo like these.",
